{"tid":1410702,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"對廢老之有用對答","createTime":"2019-08-05T02:17:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T02:27:50.000Z","uid":122031,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"21731fada15617c65cb15bd0732ca4f9e812c7ea","tid":1410702,"uid":122031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T02:17:31.000Z","msg":"辛苦哂咁多位兄弟 我都知呢排係比較燥 但係同佢地硬碰硬係無好處 所以如果俾人插可以咁對答 以下內容tg睇到轉發<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 阻住我返工<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 粗口<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我都好想返工啊<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 阻住我哋啲市民/冇人支持你㗎<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 阻乜x嘢啊<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 支持警察執法（成立獨立調查委員會）<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你咪去攪林鄭囉，攪我地啲小市民做嘜？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係林鄭搞緊小市民<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係囉，佢唔出黎喎，要求政府回應！佢月薪40萬咖<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔好搞人屋企咁冇品，人地都有屋企人，屋企人係無辜咖！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 林鄭好多屋企，唔知佢訓邊<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 林鄭成個政府都冇鬼用，淨係識搵警察出黎打人，自己就匿埋，搞到愈來愈多人出黎示威<br />\n(將責任推俾政府，強調示威者都係被逼)<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 本人撐你都變到唔撐啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 請你體諒，宜家每星期都有好多流血衝突，好多年輕人受重傷，咁落去香港就黎打仗乜都冇，堵錢堵路已經係最和平嘅方法去施壓俾政府<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 其實我哋而家唔係要爭取同意,係希望政府可以回應依家社會發生緊嘅嘢<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你唔需要撐我，撐警察就得，支持成立獨立調査委員會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 成班死癈青，淨係識攪事<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 今日好多律師會計師公務員都罷工呀，政府太過分，天怒人怨<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 如果政府真係有做嘢就唔會咁多死癈青啦，收納税人咁多錢又唔做嘢，一日到黑只係識得譴責！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 粗口<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 粗口回應<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 嘩支持政府嘅人咁暴力嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 嘩！問候我哋呢啲小市民<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你與其責備我地搞事不如責備下呢個暴力制度嘅政府<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我明嘅，你係想鬧個政府搞到啲人出黎示威<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我都好嬲呀，講左咁多次訴求，政府都漠示民意<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 車長！有人講粗口，違反香港鐵路附例呀！罰佢$5000！"},{"pid":"ab0c62c1c4580560ceefd135e2d8672fbe29ff14","tid":1410702,"uid":122031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T02:19:18.000Z","msg":"Upupup"},{"pid":"3a8213646cc4ebed18fdb16a31c86afc9cd79f29","tid":1410702,"uid":122031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T02:19:36.000Z","msg":"罷工呀"},{"pid":"87022c4ebd312db87a7a693d333b95d684f0cc40","tid":1410702,"uid":122031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T02:19:57.000Z","msg":"出黎集會啦"},{"pid":"f436177d732b48878ec6cc310deaf34e5a1ec9b8","tid":1410702,"uid":122031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T02:20:30.000Z","msg":"香港要你去捍衛啊"},{"pid":"d9765b9590c99a1f6c7725543efb36dbda6279aa","tid":1410702,"uid":122031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T02:27:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d280a218e811eb46a2cf2ad57486a7e0b6cc4302","tid":1410702,"uid":122031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T02:27:50.000Z","msg":"有禮貌啲人都到對我地無咁反感啊"}]}